{"type": "article", "id": 18591, "title": "树干路灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-07T07:52:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001532NnyxudPGBKa08Wvz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是法国设计师 Mathieu Lehanneur 新推出的路灯，正在巴黎的气候大会期间陆续安装。路灯的支柱和下面的座位都模拟了树干的形状，其实是将附近多个品种的树在一起加工而成的。这盏灯有三个云朵一样的灯罩，其中两个用来照明，第三个是面朝上的太阳能电池板，此外灯柱子上还有一个充电小孔，让路人在休息的同时也给手机充一会儿电。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001529BAfNUZP07XCYRFx6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001529Z0pNcijWDXOTy2eM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.56601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060015303lSoF9zdMYtyHjQp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.05501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001530kCd8VX6MAzZ9Kt7c.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.30562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060600153191tsM8FcjBfvwDo0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.21882641\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001532SKBmQXYFuDygJC0I.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}